attributeSource.infoString2: Keller Williams Coral Gables - Coconut Grove

data.description: FABULOUS 2 story, 5 bedroom 3 bath single family home situated on a quiet and peaceful lake and having spectacular sunsets. This gated community home has a two car garage; 1 bedroom and bath downstairs and 4 bedrooms and 2 bath upstairs; tile flooring throughout with exception of the upstairs bedrooms have beautiful Italian wood floors; very spacious and open home with plenty of light; very exclusive family oriented area; fantastic clubhouse includes pool, gym, sauna, event space. Fast access to turnpike/US1.  Minutes to shopping, dining, parks, schools and Baptist Hospital.  Central to the Florida Keys, the City of Miami and the Everglades.
